    <p class="c1 c2"><span class="c0"></span></p>
    <p class="c1"><span class="c6">Precise location permission (non-continuous)</span></p>
    <p class="c1"><span class="c0">Used for accessing the User&#39;s precise device location. This Application may collect, use, and share User location Data in order to provide location-based services. The geographic location of the User is determined in a manner that isn&#39;t continuous. This means that it is impossible for this Application to derive the exact position of the User on a continuous basis.</span>
